<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">

<h1>Hey, What's up <%= @analysis.user.username %>?</h1>

<h3>Pantari Personality Analysis for <%= @analysis.author %></h3> 

  <% if @analysis.openness == nil %>
    <h3>Every program has bugs, but this time it's probably your fault.   Either your words weren't good enough or you don't have enough of them. Do better next time.<br>
    <p>Try submitting a longer writing sample.</p>
    </h3><p><a href="new"> Try again</a> </p>
  <%else%>    

    <p>This analysis contained <strong><%= @analysis.word_count %></strong>   words.<br>  </p>  
    <p>Results in percentiles</p>
    <h3>The Big 5 Personality Traits</h3>
    <ul>  
      <p><li>agreeableness----------<%= @analysis.agreeableness %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>conscientiousness-----<%= @analysis.conscientiousness %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>extraversion------------<%= @analysis.extraversion %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>emotional range--------<%= @analysis.emotional_range %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>openness----------------<%= @analysis.openness %>%</li></p>
      </ul>
      <h3>Needs and the Necessity of Them</h3>
      <ul>
      <p><li>challenge----------------<%= @analysis.challenge %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>closeness---------------<%= @analysis.closeness %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>curiosity----------------<%= @analysis.curiosity %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>excitement--------------<%= @analysis.excitement %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>harmony----------------<%= @analysis.harmony %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>ideal---------------------<%= @analysis.ideal %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>liberty-------------------<%= @analysis.liberty %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>love----------------------<%= @analysis.love %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>practicality--------------<%= @analysis.practicality %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>self-expression---------<%= @analysis.self_expression %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>stability-----------------<%= @analysis.stability %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>structure----------------<%= @analysis.structure %>%</li></p></ul>
      <h3>The Value of Values</h3>
      <ul>
      <p><li>conservation------------<%= @analysis.conservation %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>openness-to-change---<%= @analysis.openness_to_change %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>hedonism----------------<%= @analysis.hedonism %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>self-enhancement------<%= @analysis.self_enhancement  %>%</li></p>
      <p><li>self-transcendence-----<%= @analysis.self_transcendence  %>%</li></p>
      </ul>
    <br> *Analysis should contain at least 3000 words to be accurate
  
  <form method="link" action="/personality_analyses/<%= @analysis.id %>/edit">
  <input type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-default" value="Edit Author"><br><br>
  </form>
  
  <form method="post" action="/personality_analyses/<%= @analysis.id %>/delete">
    <input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-default" value="Delete Analysis">
  </form><br>
  <a href="/analyses" class="btn btn-lg btn-default">Back to Analyses</a> 
  
  <% if @analysis.tweeter_text != nil || @analysis.person_text == nil %>
    <h3>Here are the last 200 tweets from @<%=@analysis.tweeter_username.gsub("@", "") %> </h3>
    <%= @analysis.tweeter_text unless @analysis.tweeter_text == nil%>
  <% else %>
    <h3>Here's all that stuff that <%=@analysis.author%> wrote.</h3>
    <%= @analysis.person_text.gsub("���", "'") unless @analysis.person_text == nil%>
  <%end%>
<%end%>  

